57^{\circ} 56^{\prime \prime}-58^{\circ} 7^{\prime \prime}$. Sampling of Electric Arc Furnace Dust (EAFD) at the Esfarayen Steel Factory was performed at three randomly selected locations, designated A, B, and C. At each location, five samples were collected and composited, yielding a total weight of 3 kg per location. Newly produced EAFD was categorized as sample A, slightly aged EAFD as sample B, and the oldest EAFD as sample C.

